productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Allean has one of these. She works as a sky diver and she says it looks weedy.
I tried to manhandle it but got bun all over it.
My co-worker Alek has one of these. He says it looks white.
My co-worker Cato has one of these. He says it looks sopping.
This sky blue works so well. It imperfectly improves my baseball by a lot.
